{"parse":{"title":"First Siege of Arsuf","pageid":53090722,"revid":859186081,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"summary\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Siege of Arsuf</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;\">Part of the <a href=\"/wiki/Crusade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crusade\">Crusades</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;line-height:1.5em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gustave dore crusades gerard of avesnes exposed on the walls of asur.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg/220px-Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg/330px-Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fd/Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg/440px-Gustave_dore_crusades_gerard_of_avesnes_exposed_on_the_walls_of_asur.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"956\" data-file-height=\"1210\" /></a><br />Gerard of Avesnes exposed on the walls of Arsuf. Illustration by <a href=\"/wiki/Gustave_Dor%C3%A9\" title=\"Gustave Dor\u00e9\">Gustave Dor\u00e9</a> (1877)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><table style=\"width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0\"><tbody><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Date</th><td>late October \u2013 mid-December 1099</td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Location</th><td><span class=\"location\"><a href=\"/wiki/Arsuf\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arsuf\">Arsuf</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Fatimid_Caliphate\" title=\"Fatimid Caliphate\">Fatimid Caliphate</a></span></td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Result</th><td>\nFatimid victory</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\n<span class=\"flagicon\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/23px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/35px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/45px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"113\" data-file-height=\"75\" />&#160;</span><a href=\"/wiki/Fatimid_Caliphate\" title=\"Fatimid Caliphate\">Fatimid Caliphate</a></td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n<span class=\"flagicon\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg/23px-Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg.png\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg/35px-Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg/45px-Vexillum_Regni_Hierosolymae.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"600\" data-file-height=\"400\" />&#160;</span><a href=\"/wiki/Kingdom_of_Jerusalem\" title=\"Kingdom of Jerusalem\">Kingdom of Jerusalem</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Commanders and leaders</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\n<span class=\"flagicon\"><a href=\"/wiki/Fatimid_Caliphate\" title=\"Fatimid Caliphate\"><img alt=\"Fatimid Caliphate\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/23px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/35px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/39/White_flag_3_to_2.svg/45px-White_flag_3_to_2.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"113\" data-file-height=\"75\" /></a></span> Governor of Arsuf</td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Armoiries de J\u00e9rusalem.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b5/Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg/18px-Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg.png\" width=\"18\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b5/Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg/27px-Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b5/Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg/36px-Armoiries_de_J%C3%A9rusalem.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"600\" data-file-height=\"660\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Godfrey_of_Bouillon\" title=\"Godfrey of Bouillon\">Godfrey of Bouillon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Strength</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\nUnknown</td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n3,000<sup id=\"cite_ref-FOOTNOTEStevenson190739_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-FOOTNOTEStevenson190739-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Casualties and losses</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\nUnknown</td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\nUnknown</td>